title: 19th Century French Drawings from the R. Lehman Collection (Art)
description:
19th Century French Drawings from the Robert Lehman Collection
Metropolitan | 1980 | ISBN: 0870992562 | English | PDF | 92 pages | 7.61 Mb

This exhibition of nineteenth-century French drawings continues the series that will eventually bring all the drawings in the Robert Lehman Collection to public view.

Among these eighty-five sheets are drawings in various media, including watercolor, representing the most important French masters of the century as well as lesser-known French artists
